<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-the-presence-of-sb-in-sbs-presence">in the presence of sb / in sb's presence</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>当着某人的面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He apologized to her in the presence of the whole family. 
他当着全家人的面向她道歉。</p></div></div>